00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:40.000
<v Bernstein> My dear young friends: On our last program, 

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:43.000
if you recall, we were celebrating the 

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:45.000
double anniversary of our New York 

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:47.000
Philharmonic and the Vienna Philharmonik 

