Beethoven concert is a very frequent 

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:45.000
happening. And what is the main 

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:48.000
piece on every piano recital? A Beethoven 

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:51.000
sonata. And during the last World War, 

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:53.000
what was our musical symbol for victory? 

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:58.000
Pah-pah-pah-PAH. 

